date_appr: 8 Altona diss. & reformed into 2 sch. dists. 8 & 13 each embracing same terr. that it did before consol.

No edn in 1923 up to Oct. See last yrs. Report. Boundaries of 1 Peru altered by taking therefrom all the lands formerly contained in what was prior to Oct. 6, 1923, sch. dist. No. 5 Peru 31 Ag. 1927. New dist. No. 5 Peru created.
